title: [Ta'Illistim, Linsandrych Var]
description: Just out of the shadow of a silvery blue stone gatehouse, the cobblestones fan out into a wide var, which splits off in opposite directions.  Lush, blossoming foliage lines either side of a narrow walkway that leads into a flourishing garden.  An enameled silver sign is placed next to a crystal-paned lantern hung from a carved alabaster column.
